Title: Fix "IP address family" only shown on "show more"
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1678184593
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

If you created or edited a host, the configuration option "IP address family"
was only shown, if the "show more" button of the "Network address" section was
used. This option will now always be shown.

